{"id":179186,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/09/新浪承诺将确保信息真实性/","date":"2011-09-14T16:00:06Z","modified":"2011-09-14T16:00:06Z","title":"新浪承诺将确保信息真实性","content":"<p>《华尔街日报》报导，在官方宣布打击虚假信息之后，门户网站新浪承诺将确保其网站上信息的真实性。新浪在声明中说，将积极传播社会主义核心价值体系，传播社会主义先进文化，坚决杜绝虚假有害信息的传播。新浪还说，传播社会主义先进文化对新浪微博和整个互联网行业的健康发展至关重要。本月早些时候，《人民日报》发表社论文章，敦促严格监督网络，提醒黑恶势力、敌对势力、恐怖分裂组织等都有可能通过制造虚假网络舆论来操纵民意，影响社会稳定和国家安全。<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/18526cf7/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E6%96%B0%E6%B5%AA%E6%89%BF%E8%AF%BA%E5%B0%86%E7%A1%AE%E4%BF%9D%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E7%9C%9F%E5%AE%9E%E6%80%A7&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F09%2F14%2F0714232%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E6%96%B0%E6%B5%AA%E6%89%BF%E8%AF%BA%E5%B0%86%E7%A1%AE%E4%BF%9D%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E7%9C%9F%E5%AE%9E%E6%80%A7&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F09%2F14%2F0714232%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/112924360254/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/18526cf7/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/112924360254/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/18526cf7/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=9J0x_0eOd_0:Vy1S93AreQA:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=9J0x_0eOd_0:Vy1S93AreQA:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</s